Package: ralphloop
Type: Package
Title: Persistent Iterative Loop for LLM-Driven Development
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Lazarus", "Alvarez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lazarusalvarez3@gmail.com")
Description:
    Provides a persistent, truth-based iterative development loop for
    large language models using the ellmer package. Inspired by the
    Ralph loop pattern popularized by Anthropic's Claude Code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    ellmer,
    yaml,
    glue
Suggests:
    devtools,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
